00:24:10,390 --> 00:24:12,219
Tolong bantu aku!

355
00:24:12,459 --> 00:24:14,959
Kumohon bantu aku!

356
00:24:18,860 --> 00:24:21,569
"S.M.H"

357
00:25:16,219 --> 00:25:19,229
"Di balik tabir waktu"

358
00:25:21,529 --> 00:25:24,529
Bisa persiapkan semua ini

359
00:25:24,930 --> 00:25:26,769
agar bisa diwariskan kepada An Soon Jin?

360
00:25:27,769 --> 00:25:29,170
An Soon Jin?

361
00:25:29,640 --> 00:25:33,069
Kamu sudah membantu selama bertahun-tahun, bukan?

362
00:25:35,039 --> 00:25:36,340
Kami sudah menikah.

363
00:25:37,380 --> 00:25:38,410
Apa?

364
00:25:38,809 --> 00:25:40,779
Jangan beri tahu dia soal ini.

